						               													<description>Description from the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Roll fast and think faster in this addictively simple, simply addictive dice game of quick-thinking categories! From celebrities to science, songs to sports, SCRAMBO has 30 categories for everybody to test their speed, knowledge and nerves! There are over 7,000 category combinations possible!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;SCRAMBO is for 2 or more players ages 10 and up, and plays in about 15 minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One player rolls the 5 Category Dice, featuring a total of 30 different popular categories. That player then rolls the Letter Die. The goal of each turn is to match the letter rolled to each of their 5 categories before the time is up!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After the letter is rolled, another player begins rolling the 5 Timer Dice, each of which features 2 faces with a clock icon. Players bank the dice which roll with the clock facing up, and once all 5 show clocks, the turn is over!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A player shouts &amp;quot;SCRAMBO!&amp;quot; once either of these happen:&amp;#10;1. The category player answers all 5 of their Category Dice, or&amp;#10;2. The timer player rolls 5 clocks on the Timer Dice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players score 1 point for every category answered.&amp;#10;Timer player scores 1 point if the category player leaves any dice unanswered.&amp;#10;Timer player score 3 points if they end the turn before any categories can be answered.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;First player to 20 points is the winner!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
